column2: my_plot <- ggplot(top_10_diarrhea_cases_counties, aes(x =reorder(county,total_cases), y =total_cases)) + geom_bar(stat = 'identity', fill="indianred2", color ="white")+
coord_flip() + labs(x="", y="total_cases", title = "Top 10 Counties with Diarrhea cases for children <5 Years", subtitle = "(Between Jan 2021 and June 2023)")
